definitions.definition: Of, relating to, directed toward, or situated at the front .

subdefinitions.definition: Directed against the front or at the main point or issue .

definitions.definition: Of or relating to the forehead or frontal bone .
Parallel to the main axis of the body and at right angles to the sagittal plane .
Any of the scales of a reptile that lie in the general region of the forehead , more specifically between the eyes and to the anterior of this area.
Of or relating to a weather front .

main_definition: Of, relating to, directed toward, or situated at the front .
secondary_definitions: ( anatomy ) Of or relating to the forehead or frontal bone .
( anatomy ) Parallel to the main axis of the body and at right angles to the sagittal plane .
( zootomy ) Any of the scales of a reptile that lie in the general region of the forehead , more specifically between the eyes and to the anterior of this area.
( meteorology ) Of or relating to a weather front .
